<div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
        <h1>About Me</h1>

        <hr>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                        <div class="skill">
                            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                            <div class="progress">
                                <div 
                                    class="progress-bar progress-barpstriped bg-warning"
                                    role="progressbar"
                                    aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                                    aria-valuemax="100"
                                    style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                                ></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <p>
                    Add some information about the album below, the author, or any other background context. Make it a few sentences long so folks can pick up some informative tidbits. Then, link them off to some social networking sites or contact information.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Add some information about the album below, the author, or any other background context. Make it a few sentences long so folks can pick up some informative tidbits. Then, link them off to some social networking sites or contact information.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    <button
                        class="btn btn-primary"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#jobHistory"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controller="jobHistory"
                    >
                        Job History
                    </button>
                    
                    <button
                        class="btn btn-primary"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#education"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controller="education"
                    >
                        Education
                    </button>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Job 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            Job 2
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="collapse" id="education">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            school 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                            school 2
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
